WEBVTT

00:01.126 --> 00:02.668
It's Aurelia.
She was bearing a child.

00:02.836 --> 00:03.836
She tried to end it.

00:04.003 --> 00:05.462
We could repair
the perforation.

00:05.630 --> 00:06.797
Was it yours?

00:06.965 --> 00:08.382
You won't be able to bear
a child.

00:08.550 --> 00:09.842
I already got one.

00:10.010 --> 00:12.511
Where did all this come from?
I insist you answer!

00:12.679 --> 00:14.221
Take this fine lady

00:14.389 --> 00:16.097
back up to the wards
where she belongs.

00:16.265 --> 00:17.766
A ball?
In our home?

00:17.934 --> 00:19.476
Emmaand Alice
will be distracting

00:19.644 --> 00:22.229
those two blue bellies,
keeping them busy at the ball

00:22.397 --> 00:24.148
while I slip in
and make my way here.

00:24.315 --> 00:25.774
The oath is
a matter of allegiance.

00:25.942 --> 00:28.485
As the provost marshal,
you could grant me a reprieve.

00:28.653 --> 00:29.820
I can't go back.

00:29.988 --> 00:31.321
Tell Alice
that I love her.

